<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4306608>
    dc:description "FIGURE 5. Andricus forni n. sp.: (a) forewing, (b) frontal head of female with clear area around clypeus, (c) galls with details." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4306608/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4306600>
    dc:description "FIGURE 1. Head of Andricus forni n. sp.: (a) female in frontal view, (b) male in frontal view, (c) female in dorsal view, (d) male in dorsal view, (e) female in posterior view, (f) male in posterior view." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4306600/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4306602>
    dc:description "FIGURE 2. Andricus forni n. sp., antennae: (a) female antenna with detail of last flagellomeres, F11 and F12 completely separated, b) female antenna with detail of last flagellomeres, F11 and F12 incompletely separated, (c) male with detail of F1." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4306602/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4306604>
    dc:description "FIGURE 3. Andricus forni n. sp., mesosoma: (a) female in dorsal view, (b) female in lateral view, (c) female propodeum, (d) male propodeum." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4306604/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4306606>
    dc:description "FIGURE 4. Andricus forni n. sp., metasoma and details of micropunctures: (a) female, (b) male." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4306606/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4306610>
    dc:description "FIGURE 6. Bayesian majority-rule consensus tree of 433bp of cytochrome b sequence derived from Asian Andricus species. Numbers at nodes indicate posterior probability support; major clades mentioned in the text are indicated by the letters A–D." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4306610/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

